      What are the 3 types of lighting?

      What are the best lights for living room?
      While living room lighting is a personal choice, soft white and warm white are ideal for living rooms, as they emit a warmer, golden glow. Cool white and daylight bulbs, on the other hand, tend to be a little harsher and reminiscent of commercial spaces.

      Description

      Lights Poxleitner-Bokan, known mononymously as Lights, is a Canadian musician, singer, and songwriter. She is known for singles "Drive My Soul", "February Air", "Ice", "Second Go", "Toes", "My Boots" and "Up We Go", which have charted within the top ninety on the Canadian Hot 100. Wikipedia
      Born: 1987 (age 35 years), Timmins, Canada
      Music group: Young Artists for Haiti (2010 2010)
      Spouse: Beau Bokan (m. 2012)
      Full name: Lights Poxleitner-Bokan
      Genres: Alternative/Indie, Dance/Electronic
      Parents: Virginia Poxleitner, Eric Poxleitner
